README

Requirements:
1. .env file with:
# VAPI token : 
VAPI_TOKEN="abc"

# Gemini or any LLM model to use for evaluating results:
GEMINI_STUDIO_API_KEY=xyz

# VAPI phone number (caller phone ID as string)
VAPI_PHONE_ID="phone_string"


How to run the code:
- git clone repo
- cd to repo
(cd voice-agent-test)

- source venv/bin/activate

- python3 ./voice_agent_test.py test_data.json


Sample test run is file test_run.txt